Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you wanted to see me...\Nright, pirate lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to hear the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I saw Nico Robin with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... she is one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your words no longer mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Nico Robin again now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits for Mr. Iceberg's\Nattack were the Straw Hat pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, Water-Water Newspaper, will buy\Nany information on their sightings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again. Let me see Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from the bedroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet on a silly hope that I might\Nbe able to get closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture... all the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:02:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to talk to\NIceberg-san by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He said he really saw Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be...! Why would Robin\Ndo something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:26.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:29.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:40.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:51.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:58.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:05.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:12.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:20.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:27.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:35.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:58.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:06.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:16.03,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Eternal Farewell? Nico Robin,\Nthe Woman Who Draws Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! We're here!\NGrandma Kokoro! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Seven... It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing a mask is prohibited today\Nwhen you get on board the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show me your ticket and your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my own face! My own face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kokoro-san! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We're after the\NStraw Hats who're the culprits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Iceberg-san's attempted assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg's assassination? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... Nooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling! I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We've landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "We've landed" me! I thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could we have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who said that\Nwe couldn't use the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because we didn't want them to find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you didn't have to jump off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not that shipwright with a square nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine. At least it did get us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was okay, then don't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this may be kinda bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad? What's bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island's geography and the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this much wind blowing,\Nif the atmospheric pressure drops,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a typhoon might come through here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town is called the City of Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it can be a weak point\Nthat could easily lead to flood damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It bothers me a little,\Nso I'll check into it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go back to the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! How's it going, Blueno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going super?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "I think"?!\NYou sure are an indecisive guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the usual! Fill them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just refill them! Cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you run a bar\Nwith such a stingy notion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you take money from your customers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a million Berries\Nleft over from shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got that much money from yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shameful! How uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I didn't spend it all yesterday...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! You guys! You're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All your alcohol is on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink as much as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's our Franky! You're generous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man! The face of the\NWater Seven underworld! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's more on the floor over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Blueno! Where's my cola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're doing well, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag Kokoro! That was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a statue of a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it okay to get a\Nrefill for my juice, Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bar. It's not a place for kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Okay, then. Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm doing well, but I'm\Nfeeling gloomy. I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling terrible this week,\Nthanks to that damn pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the refilled cola! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuel! Fuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:09:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes! Here it comes! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've revived! That jerk! Next time\NI see him, I'll beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, old hag, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that right? No wonder the wind is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done getting your house ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my house is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing that could sink,\Nso I have no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to have a drink with Iceberg,\Nbut I heard he got shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it was the pirates' doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La and the townspeople\Nare furious right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates' doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously think that's the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say whatever comes to mind, old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg has been getting nagged all this\Ntime by the World Government, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then, what? Are you saying\Nthat official, Corgy, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tubby isn't an assassin type!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Shadowy incidents are the work of CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about it, Blueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just heard some rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Common folk sure do like to believe\Nrumors of things like nonexistent organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish... It does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they never show themselves, since their\Nunit works secretly in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that confidence coming from?\NDo you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's just a rumor, then!\NDon't mess with--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It always being a rumor is the scary part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They eliminate people without anyone noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you meddle with them, you're dead meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. The job we had\Nto do yesterday went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although naturally you're now\Nbeing pursued by the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is... tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll infiltrate Iceberg's\Nresidence one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If worst comes to worst, it's okay\Nto eliminate all the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the disciples of this\NTom guy who originally had it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg is the only one currently alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much he plays innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of CP9, we'll take\Nit away tonight for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear in mind that this is a mission for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following the Aqua Laguna warning\Nissued for the entire island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the shipbuilding factory docks\Non the shipbuilding island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be opened as evacuation centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Large crowds are expected,\Nso please evacuate ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, since Dock #1 is\Ncurrently in a dangerous state...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll put the iron board on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have everything you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we do. Let's evacuate to the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold on a bit. I'd better\Nfill the gap good with hempen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the inside of our house gets flooded,\Neverything will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tie that side, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the wind is starting to get strong!\NGet ready for waves soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! If we're taking our time,\Nassassin pirates will show up too this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure he came this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should still be around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you guys go search over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I being chased after? I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the reason they've\Nbeen chasing after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassination culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bites. I can't even go\Nback to the inn like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Who is it over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! I found a suspicious guy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, landlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Those pirates have been\Nstaying at this inn since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were there until just a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since they've still got a\Nlot of luggage in their room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! You guys, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you, let's go\Nsearch this area together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, make sure you leave\Nno stone unturned to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really their ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Straw Hats' pirate flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they've already abandoned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is all beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they aren't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much stuff left inside the ship.\NThis ship definitely is abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something happening in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you find them?\N--No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think everyone's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Craftsmen are everywhere in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Chopper and Sanji-kun are okay,\Nsince their faces are still unknown, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea train is still in service...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the afternoon train has already left,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's another one that\Ndeparts at night in this bad weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,11 PM, leaving for Enies Lobby...\NThe sea train is pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Any information on the pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we capture even one of those three\Nwhose faces are known and squeeze him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of the gang will be identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Before the waves get high!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Robin got on the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she did, things can't get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Water Seven is\Nalready too big to handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if... I did something\Nto upset her at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy... There's no way that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen a pretty woman like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that... The pretty woman who's 20\Nyears older than in that picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had, I would've told either the paper\Ncompany or Galley-La immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think she's an assassin...\NWhat a surprise, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine if you wanna look for\Nthe culprits, but you should evacuate soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll be swallowed by Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going wrong for all of us, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Luffy and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's fine. The one I'm\Nworried about is Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the town is becoming quite empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is gradually getting stronger, too.\NPeople have started evacuating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin-chan! Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scent... Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I said wait! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't be reckless!\NWhat on earth is going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting to run so sudden... ly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where have you been?!\NWe looked all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worried about you!\NNow, let's go back to the inn together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot has happened while you've\Nbeen gone. I'll explain in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this distance is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'll be right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... return to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're parting ways here... in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you saying, Robin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. You're thinking about the\Nnewspaper, right? Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and being falsely accused of a\Ncrime often happens to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for pinning an\Nunreasonable crime on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the article is telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really was me who infiltrated\Nthe mayor's residence last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I carry a darkness within me\Nthat you guys don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This darkness will destroy you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:20:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organizations Nico Robin had\Nsomething to do with up until today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all got annihilated... except for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, I'm pinning this\Ncrime on you and planning to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?! Why are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I'm doing it... It's something\Nyou don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! I don't get what you're saying!\NWhat happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I only spent a short\Ntime with you, after today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being nice to a person like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Robin-chan! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it time to settle\Nwhether Robin is friend or foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's suddenly changed because\Nof the masked man she was with!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That man is\Nmaking her do bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy is Robin's real friend,\Nthen that would be misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capture Robin!\NThe Determination of the Straw Hats"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
